Read the active loading and rasterization settings with `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::GetReleasePolicy`, `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::IsSynchronousLoading`, `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::IsFrameCacheEnabled`, `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::GetRenderScale`, `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::IsRedrawOnScaleDown`, `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::IsRedrawOnScaleUp`, and `Dali::Ui::LottieAnimationView::IsNotifyAfterRasterizationEnabled`.

